{"tid":2070754,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局資助全港中小學生每人$100買書 但書單内7成書來自中資出版集團","createTime":"2020-06-19T10:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T12:26:33.000Z","uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b78c3644136ef91ce1e0dd215d628d34fbb74d98","tid":2070754,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:38:04.000Z","msg":"教育界立法會議員葉建源表示，教育局推出的暑期閱讀贈閱圖書試行計劃，資助中小學校每位學生100元買書，要求學校三個星期內，在教育局提供的748本書目名單中選書，<span style=\"color: red;\">發現當中7成來自同一個中資出版集團，嚴重失衡，質疑有利益輸送</span>，業界亦有意見指計劃打破一貫，學校可靈活購買不同種類書籍的採購規則，包括英文書及電子書，要求當局交代，和讓學校在不限制出版商及書目下選書。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1314131&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1314131%26csid%3D261_341&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=1a170eca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1314131&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ba59725bd297c6a262b565d4a724a9a34b4933","tid":2070754,"uid":30215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:38:47.000Z","msg":"毅進星 $100"},{"pid":"adfd83d1df57c14f5b7ceaaeb55a516955f35e40","tid":2070754,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f28788793c471f752c03996d389bb1acc12017c","tid":2070754,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:41:13.000Z","msg":"港共<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(騙徒)</span>嘅手法層出不窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d67ad5c3b4c56912000695c7a4c206750aee01c","tid":2070754,"uid":200663,"like":0,"disl